The '''A476''' is a main road in [[Wales]], linking [[Llanelli]] with the [[A483 road|A483]], the [[Swansea]] to [[Manchester]] [[Trunk road]] near the market town of [[Llandeilo]].

Settlements served by the road include:
*[[Llanelli]]
*[[Panteg]]
*[[Llannon]]
*[[Upper Tumble]]
*[[Cross Hands]]
*[[Gorslas]]
*[[Carmel, Carmarthenshire|Carmel]]
*[[Golden Grove, Carmarthenshire|Golden Grove]]
*[[Ffairfach]] ({{convert|1/2|mi}} south of Llandeilo)

